Example spatial dataset 3 from Wu et al.

spatial_data_3.Rd

A SpatialExperiment containing a total of 1322 spots from sample CID44971

Usage

data("spatial_data_3")

Format

A SpatialExperiment with 36601 genes and 1322 spots

Source

Wu SZ, Al-Eryani G, Roden DL, Junankar S et al. A single-cell and spatially resolved atlas of human breast cancers. Nat Genet 2021 Sep;53(9):1334-1347. PMID: 34493872
